Package in.kncsolutions.dhelm.candlebasic

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BlackCandle
    According to litarature a Black candle is made of Black body, i.e closing price is lower than the opening price.The upper and lower shadows are required.
    BlackMarubozu
    According to literature a Black marubozu candle is made of Black body, i.e closing price is lower than the opening price.There are no upper and lower shadows.
    BlackSpinningTop
    According to litarature a Black spinning top candle is made of Black body, i.e closing price is lower than the opening price.There must be one shadow present.
    ClosingBlackMarubozu
    According to litarature a closing Black marubozu candle is made of Black body, i.e closing price is lower than the opening price.There is an upper shadow but there is no lower shadow.
    ClosingWhiteMarubozu
    According to litarature a closing white marubozu candle is made of white body, i.e closing price is higher than the opening price.There are no upper shadow but there is lower shadow.
    Doji
    According to litarature a Doji candle is a candle where opening and closing prices are equal.
    DragonFlyDoji
    According to litarature a DragonFly Doji candle is a candle where opening and closing prices are equal.
    FourPriceDoji
    According to litarature a Four Price Doji candle is a candle where opening, closing, high and low prices are equal.
    GraveStoneDoji
    According to litarature a Gravestone Doji candle is a candle where opening and closing prices are equal.
    HighWave
    According to litarature a high wave candle is made of white or black body.There must be one shadow present.
    LongBlackCandle

    According to litarature a Long Legged Doji candle is a candle where opening and closing prices are equal.
    LongWhiteCandle

    ShortBlackCandle

    ShortWhiteCandle

    WhiteCandle
    According to literature a white candle is made of white body, i.e closing price is higher than the opening price.The upper and lower shadows are required.
    WhiteMarubozu
